---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const openclawContent = await getCollection('openclaw-content');
const openclawPlatform = await getCollection('openclaw-platform');
---

<BaseLayout title="홈">
  <div class="home">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-emoji">🚀</div>
      <h1><em>OpenClaw</em> 플랫폼팀</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        오픈클로 = 지피터스<br/>
        콘텐츠 · 플랫폼 · 강의 — 3축이 서로의 퍼널이 되는 플라이휠
      </p>
    </section>

    <h2 class="section-title">📁 프로젝트</h2>
    <section class="projects-grid">
      <a href="/openclaw-platform" class="project-card" style="--project-color: #6366f1;">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-icon">🤖</span>
          <h2>openclaw-platform</h2>
          <span class="project-count">{openclawPlatform.length}편</span>
        </div>
        <p>플랫폼 전략, 채널 설계, 봇 코칭, KPI, 회의록, 덕후방 인사이트, 보고서</p>
        <div class="project-sub">
          <span>📂 meetings/ · duckhu-archive/ · reports/</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/openclaw-content" class="project-card" style="--project-color: #f59e0b;">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-icon">✍️</span>
          <h2>openclaw-content</h2>
          <span class="project-count">{openclawContent.length}편</span>
        </div>
        <p>콘텐츠 전략, SNS 채널 전략, SEO 선점</p>
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .home { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
  .hero { text-align: center; padding: 60px 0 32px; }
  .hero-emoji { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-desc { font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }

  .section-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 32px; }

  .projects-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; padding-bottom: 80px; }

  .project-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-card);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--project-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .project-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--project-color);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .project-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .project-icon { font-size: 28px; }
  .project-header h2 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); flex: 1; font-family: var(--font-mono); }
  .project-count { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); background: var(--accent-bg); padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 10px; }

  .project-card > p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .project-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .project-header h2 { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>
